item.title: Product of Impatience grown for a Product.
item.dc:creator: BoingBoing
item.description:
Created Zomklein based on the zombie base entity.
Created Grunt based on Combine guards-I had to create my own base but most of the code looks like combine guards.
Created Houndeye based on Antlion Guard, then on custom base. There is no ‘hidden Houndeye’ script.
Created Bullsquid based on Antlion Guard, then on custom base with spitter-grenade.
Added crossbow scope fade in/out
Changed shotgun skin, added trace effect to shotgun.
Changed SMG1 skins, added ironsight (forgot to demo in video)
View rotates when you strafe.
Head bops when you walk forward.
Ceil Sentry based on barnacle/turret.
Turret based on ground turret.
Baby headcrabs = headcrabs with smaller hull/model.
Level taken from Freeman’s Mind ep 11 since I never played Half Life, I don’t know the level name. Recreated it myself.
Tesla/Vortigaunt charge effect for NPC spawning.
Custom HEV skin.

All NPC’s and Weapons were scripted from other portions of npc’s or weapons and do not replace the original NPC or weapon.

I think I broke some rule about feeding trolls and “quiting” forums. Forever.
Anywho, I expected the community to be like facepunch and my expectations were off-way off. Of course I don’t want to be near people who call other people drama queens and use smiley-macros to waste a whole post that could have said something worthy.

With all due respect you internet cancer people should be put to an end for the benefit and further development of all woman-kind. You’re like Christianity.
